{"tid":2301364,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"long distance的未來爸爸（樹窿mode）","createTime":"2020-11-26T08:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T22:25:02.000Z","uid":158760,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e2caa3b33321712a97b90819f990e8c80de58a40","tid":2301364,"uid":158760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:55:35.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n如果你起我底嘅話，你會知道我而家嘅女朋友係歐洲人，七月份嘅時候佢大左肚，決定咗去歐洲嗰邊生，無他，佢其實係愛我既但係我依家唔係好搵到錢所以佢需要係佢屋企人果邊食同住。<br />\n<br />\n咁我自己都因為做爸爸嘅關係走咗去考紀律部隊（唔撚係PC），考晒所有試架啦，依家只係喺度等結果。<br />\n<br />\n上星期送左佢機，自己一個人嘅時候先至發現，做咗爸爸嘅，就算一個人有幾孤獨都唔會有興趣去搵其他女仔。原來改變一個人可以咁簡單。<br />\n<br />\n搵唔到錢？諗辦法囉<br />\n想考紀律部隊但唔夠fit？我日日都做gym，最難既體能果關都pass埋，關關難過關關過，4關？冇事既盡左力就算啦。<br />\n<br />\n唔夠好，就努力做好，做唔好，就搵方法改變下自己再不斷試。點解有一種莫名其妙嘅動力不斷令我變得更加成熟更加有責任感。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始有冇後悔有BB?有，但當佢越來越大嘅時候我諗法都會不斷變。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到而家呢一刻其實開始有啲迷失唔係好知道自己做緊乜嘢，但係我知道要盡自己嘅能力去照顧好佢地。<br />\n<br />\nSorry我講野講到一嚿嚿其實係因為我心情仲未平伏到。黎呻下，比連登仔屌下都好，可能屌屌下會醒返知自己做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">冇錢咪撚生仔</span>"},{"pid":"ea680e3a1f55fce9861438e18f2bc2a03782d565","tid":2301364,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:59:07.000Z","msg":"哦 係咩"},{"pid":"51cb352f8c93fa5cadd2ce603285de0cd282cdba","tid":2301364,"uid":158760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea680e3a1f55fce9861438e18f2bc2a03782d565","tid":2301364,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:59:07.000Z","msg":"哦 係咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:02:13.000Z","msg":"只係想呻下，由個post沉，thx。"},{"pid":"0f9b07bce5c31750814d4c9b92e7b36286e5ee5f","tid":2301364,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"點解唔過去搵野做貴陪佢"},{"pid":"1c7eac45ecaafb16ec049e0a9ca95532a0d4fcd0","tid":2301364,"uid":222513,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"希望你考到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b24946be7f91c196c51a26a6d7bedc8a8384e29","tid":2301364,"uid":158760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f9b07bce5c31750814d4c9b92e7b36286e5ee5f","tid":2301364,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"點解唔過去搵野做貴陪佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:11:11.000Z","msg":"等埋個試先<br />\n如果搵到錢，搵返十年八年係果邊買到樓就移民⋯<br />\n果邊一間standard stand-alone house都賣緊差唔多兩球"},{"pid":"83cef55a8e061178d7f97b02fbbf83c00aac07de","tid":2301364,"uid":158760,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c7eac45ecaafb16ec049e0a9ca95532a0d4fcd0","tid":2301364,"uid":222513,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"希望你考到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:12:11.000Z","msg":"多謝你咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66fc38ee49d405bb8e2d6cf8a0f5206e32b8b55","tid":2301364,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"得公務員先搵到錢 明了"},{"pid":"f860c1ba9c1126f03bdde1dfa8fe352656008f68","tid":2301364,"uid":158760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a66fc38ee49d405bb8e2d6cf8a0f5206e32b8b55","tid":2301364,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"得公務員先搵到錢 明了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"我得中7畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經唔係睇長遠了<br />\n而係諗緊佢生左之後我可以點樣負返責任<br />\n<br />\n做左老豆，但又冇撚用搵唔到錢果種感覺其實都幾唔知點面對。<br />\n錢唔重要，但你唔可以冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8adc38151fcfeac94adca9407576def85309c5","tid":2301364,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09: